snippet.title: GW15/16 - Chelsea Double Defence Hammered! - FPL Family (Fantasy Premier League)
snippet.description:
Lee and Sam are back, looking over all the weekend's FPL action!

City and Liverpool both gain ground on Chelsea, who come unstuck to another excellent West Ham home performance. Elsewhere, Spurs and Newcastle's revivals continues under new bosses Conte and Howe.

If you're new to the channel - WELCOME! If you've been here before, a warm welcome back and you know what to expect - FPL analysis of all the weekend's games and a look ahead to next week's key player targets and transfers for our FPL teams.
